  "text": "The system should not only be a platform based on Grid [CITATION_1] infrastructure for implementing DDM techniques but also it should provide new distributed algorithms for exploring very large and distributed datasets. The first step of the development of these algorithms concern distributed clustering techniques which are well studied by the community in comparison with distributed association rules and distributed classification. In this section, we present some important DDM algorithms of clustering, frequent items set generation that can be integrated in the system. Other traditional DM algorithms such as K-means clustering and a range of its variants are also implemented in our system.",
